HEADWORD: Allowableness
<hw>Al*low"a*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
allowable; permissibleness; lawfulness; exemption from prohibition or
impropriety.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

